12 amending 47 O.S. 2021, Section 6-207, as amended by
Section 70, Chapter 282, O.S.L. 2022 (47 O.S. Supp.
13 2023, Section 6-207), which relates to authority to
deny application for or cancel license for certain
14 ailments; deleting certain reporting requirement;
